Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,FAREWELL TO THE FATHER
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine, do you have any strength left\Nto throw me up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.73,0:02:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.90,0:02:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You trying to fight in the air\Nwon't make any difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.20,0:02:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.61,0:02:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The same as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.53,0:02:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of man would watch\Nsomeone die like that and do nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.34,0:02:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.22,0:02:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet! The timing is everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.61,0:02:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:02:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.53,0:03:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You filthy trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.29,0:03:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Your pitiful attacks won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.17,0:03:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai! Use that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.60,0:03:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not as strong as Baran's,\Nbut it's still a Legendary Dark Blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.89,0:03:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So that was his plan from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.03,0:03:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel, are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.62,0:03:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll heal you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai, finish it in one shot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.79,0:03:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not even the Dark Armour Blade\Ncan endure your power for long.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.25,0:04:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! This'll work!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.85,0:04:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I could tell when our blades crossed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.73,0:04:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That weapon isn't as strong\Nas my Demon Dragon Blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.07,0:04:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll shatter it in one blow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,with my ultimate attack, Gigabreak!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.78,0:04:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not a true Gigabreak!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The spell you just used was Raiden!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.67,0:04:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.09,0:04:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have enough Magic Power\Nto use Gigaden anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.09,0:04:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's the same spell...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.72,0:04:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll win!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.35,0:04:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A Raiden spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.93,0:04:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,With my power...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.19,0:04:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and Master's attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:05:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and Hyunckel's blade...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.98,0:05:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All his power is in the blade!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.94,0:05:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.07,0:05:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the all of the memories\Nthat Popp restored.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.20,0:05:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'll hit you with!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.34,0:05:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't they using their attacks?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Because they both know\Ntheir next attack will be their last.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever offers the slightest opening\Nwill lose this fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.90,0:06:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good luck, Dai.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.36,0:06:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For Popp, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.08,0:06:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's no good.\NHe's not responding to my Zaoraru spell.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.45,0:06:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At this rate...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.42,0:06:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please! Come back to us, Popp!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.02,0:07:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.44,0:07:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I die?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.15,0:07:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I used Megante, so obviously...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Megante?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Baran?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.03,0:07:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.33,0:07:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So if this is the afterlife, he went\Nto a different afterlife or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.09,0:07:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.38,0:07:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.30,0:07:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're... Gome?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.35,0:07:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.35,0:07:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what do you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.84,0:07:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Gome's talking. I guess\Nanything's possible in the afterlife.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.98,0:07:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, does that mean you're dead, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, don't go that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.36,0:07:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll enter the Land of the Dead\Nand you won't be able to come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.58,0:07:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you say that,\Nmy feet keep moving and won't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.04,0:08:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a grip, Popp! You can't die here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.05,0:08:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We've come all this way together!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.80,0:08:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If you die, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.89,0:08:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.55,0:08:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Gome. But it's over for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.31,0:08:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a miracle I lived this long.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.64,0:08:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,My strength could only take me so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.49,0:08:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid Popp! You weakling!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.29,0:08:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.73,0:09:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He fell for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate you, Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't even avenged Master Aban\Nand you're giving up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.37,0:09:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a weakling, Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.50,0:09:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you little...! I'm not letting\Na crybaby like you call me a weakling!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.88,0:09:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried as hard as I could!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.96,0:09:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.38,0:09:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.84,0:09:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have my battle experience!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.98,0:09:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai's still...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.73,0:09:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,fighting alone out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And yet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.71,0:10:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you're abandoning him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pathetic! You're just a weakling!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.85,0:10:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch your mouth, Stupid Gome.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.53,0:10:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.23,0:10:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.07,0:10:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I may be dead, but I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.65,0:10:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.74,0:10:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.50,0:10:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Fall to my Gigabreak!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.70,0:10:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.58,0:10:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never abandon Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.94,0:11:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Impossible! A corpse cast a spell?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.24,0:11:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.04,0:11:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Aban Strash!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.95,0:12:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,A-A draw?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.97,0:12:27.55,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}ABAN STRASH{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.97,0:12:32.56,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}GIGABREAK{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.48,0:12:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.57,0:12:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.53,0:12:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.53,0:12:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.08,0:12:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.04,0:12:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.38,0:12:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's thanks to you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.46,0:13:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dark Armour Blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.89,0:13:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Even an immortal Dark Blade\Ncannot be restored with its blade gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.30,0:13:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dark Blade is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.31,0:13:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.73,0:13:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Your life is more valuable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.07,0:13:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.02,0:13:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.07,0:13:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Popp is all right as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.86,0:13:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.24,0:13:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.20,0:13:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp... can't be resurrected.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.12,0:13:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible! He just...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! He cast a spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.80,0:13:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand why that happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But, my Zaoraru spell didn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I wasn't strong enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.14,0:13:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.27,0:14:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Say it isn't true, Popp.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.81,0:14:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.52,0:14:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Open your eyes! Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.87,0:14:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.22,0:14:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Baran?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.61,0:14:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't bother bluffing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.54,0:14:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you don't have\Na bit of strength left.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:15:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Like myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.01,0:15:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}His heart has definitely stopped.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.72,0:15:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And yet, how...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.93,0:15:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did his feelings for his friend{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.19,0:15:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}cause this dead boy's body to move?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.81,0:15:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is such a miracle possible?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.98,0:15:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How ironic.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.23,0:15:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The power of Dragons,\Nmagic of Darklings, and heart of humans.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.45,0:15:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Of the three gifts\Ngranted to a Dragon Knight,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.25,0:15:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}for the human heart\NI cast aside as useless...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.58,0:15:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to deal such crushing blows to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.64,0:16:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.28,0:16:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Dino, I have nothing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.54,0:16:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Take the path that you believe is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.79,0:16:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,However, this world has no use\Nfor two Dragon Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.05,0:16:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Once my blade is restored\Nand my wounds healed...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.13,0:16:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,we shall settle this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.09,0:16:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You're returning to the Dark Army?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.26,0:16:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I no longer care about the Dark Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.01,0:16:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If you defeat me,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.06,0:16:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,you can go on to destroy\Nthe Dark Army for the humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.89,0:16:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I win...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.11,0:16:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I will wipe out the humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.32,0:16:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still saying that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.82,0:16:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late to change my ways.\NThis is just how it is for adults.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.83,0:16:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You stubborn idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.58,0:17:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Say what you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.63,0:17:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.14,0:17:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He's alive again! He has a pulse!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.35,0:17:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.98,0:17:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The boy is tougher than he looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.48,0:17:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first and last time\NI offer a gift to an enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.86,0:17:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time we meet, I won't hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.07,0:17:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Dino!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.62,0:17:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.20,0:17:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.91,0:17:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been warned!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.71,0:17:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Baran has regained his human heart.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.13,0:18:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why, to atone for his sins,\Nhe wants his own son to take him down.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.72,0:18:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He truly is tragically powerful\Nand ever alone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.57,0:18:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the worst possible outcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Baran survived\Nand Dai's powers have begun to awaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.37,0:18:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.75,0:18:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.50,0:18:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark Commander Hadorra.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.42,0:18:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,His Majesty, Dark King Ban summons you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra, raise your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.26,0:18:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Raise your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.52,0:18:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I beg for forgiveness, King Ban!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.52,0:18:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Baran's failure\Nis my responsibility as his superior!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.36,0:18:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,When he returns, I shall make sure to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.82,0:18:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.44,0:18:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Baran will likely never return.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.41,0:19:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Considering his personality,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.79,0:19:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt he'll do anything\Nunless it involves Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.58,0:19:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Baran's failure
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.50,0:19:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,is your crime for hiding that Dai was\Na Dragon Knight even from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.46,0:19:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the result\Nof your petty little games!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.51,0:19:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Baran is the only being in the world\Nwho has the power to resist me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.44,0:19:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Convincing him to become an ally\Nwas not an easy task.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.90,0:19:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll say it once more, raise your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.71,0:19:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a tolerant man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.71,0:19:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I will forgive up to three failures.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.75,0:19:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.92,0:20:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you've cost us Romos Kingdom\Nand Papunica kingdom,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.01,0:20:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}allowing two of our Legion Commanders\Nto join the other side.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.48,0:20:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And on Valge Island...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.81,0:20:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}despite leading an army,\Nyou failed to kill Dai.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.49,0:20:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, this incident with Baran...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.95,0:20:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.87,0:20:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I did not forget\Nthat you slew Aban, the Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.01,0:20:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra, this is your last chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.18,0:20:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,When you next appear before me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.81,0:20:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,if Dai and his friends\Nhave not been wiped out,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.39,0:20:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,my third finger shall drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.82,0:20:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.99,0:21:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, my king!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.70,0:21:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Hadorra, shall stake my life on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.12,0:21:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.33,0:21:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My king!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.21,0:21:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't we just kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.38,0:21:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I have given him the ultimate body.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.27,0:21:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If he cannot win,\Nthen the weakness is in his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.64,0:21:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Driven to desperation,\Nhe may actually prove his worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.82,0:21:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We can kill him anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.74,0:21:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing, King Ban.\NYou've thought of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.87,0:21:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,King Ban, hooray! Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.53,0:21:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us sit back and enjoy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.33,0:21:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the final charge of the Hadorra Legion.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.34,0:22:07.30,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tatoe akuma ni seiron kazashite\Nmukatte mitemo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.34,0:22:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if you face the devil\NWith logic on your side{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.47,0:22:11.26,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}sore wa akumade seitouka\Nsashite chigai wa naikamo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.47,0:22:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It may just be a rationalization{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.43,0:22:15.35,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ima mo ima mo yureteiru kedo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.43,0:22:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even now, even now I waver{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.52,0:22:19.40,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}bokura wa dokomade yukuno{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.52,0:22:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How far will we go?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.56,0:22:22.69,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tenshi no sasayaki nimo nita\Nkoe ga kikoeta{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.56,0:22:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I heard a voice like an angel's whisper{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.86,0:22:26.61,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hatamata petenshi no mayakashi\Nhitokiwa mimi ni hibiiteita{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.86,0:22:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe it was an imposter's illusion\NIt still rang in my ears{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.78,0:22:30.32,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ai ni hiai ni sarasare nagara{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.78,0:22:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Exposed to love and sorrow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.49,0:22:34.62,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hokori mamire michi no tochu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.49,0:22:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On the path strewn with pride{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.33,0:22:38.67,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kiete wa ukabu touhikou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.33,0:22:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fleeting moments of cowardice{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.21,0:22:42.46,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nomikonda SOS{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.21,0:22:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The SOS I held back{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.05,0:22:48.05,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}furueru te wo nigirishimeta{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.05,0:22:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I clenched my trembling fist{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.63,0:22:53.64,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tatta hitotsu no chiisana yakusoku ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.63,0:22:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That single little promise{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.81,0:22:57.43,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}honno sasaina omoidetachi ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.81,0:22:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those trivial little memories{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.60,0:22:59.73,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}itsumade tattemo kono mune wo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.60,0:22:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're still in my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.90,0:23:03.90,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kogashi tsuzukeru tomoshibi ni naru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.90,0:23:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As embers that keep me burning{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.07,0:23:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A single transparent beam of light{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.07,0:23:08.40,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tada hitosuji no toumei na hikari ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.57,0:23:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lights the way before me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.57,0:23:11.57,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}me no mae wo terashite yuku{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.74,0:23:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There is little that I can do{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.74,0:23:16.25,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}boku ni dekiru koto wa ikutsu mo naisa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.41,0:23:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just keep on to the future\NI managed to grasp through my faith{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.41,0:23:22.46,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shinjinuita saki ni te ni shita mirai wo\Nsusunde yuke{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.06,0:23:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After the battle with Baran,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.10,0:23:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai and friends stop by Meruru's house,\Nbut the Dark Army offers no rest.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.48,0:23:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The next assassin is the desperate Hadorra,\Nwith one last chance from Dark King Ban,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.24,0:23:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and Zaboera, the Mystic Bishop.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.91,0:23:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.53,0:23:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Zaboera's Scheme"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.49,0:23:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i0}
